{{歐洲聯盟政治}}
'''欧洲投资银行'''（{{lang-en|European Investment Bank}}；{{lang-fr|Banque européenne d'investissement}}；{{lang-de|Europäische Investitionsbank}}）是[[歐洲聯盟|歐洲聯盟]]的[[投資銀行|投資銀行]]，由[[歐盟成員國|歐盟成員國]]擁有<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://www.ebrd.com/downloads/news/MoU_EC-EIB-EIF-EBRD_Final_MB_formatting.pdf|title=Memorandum Of Understanding Between The European Commission, The European Investment Bank Together With The European Investment Fund, And The European Bank For Reconstruction And Development In Respect Of Cooperation Outside The European Union|publisher=European Investment Bank|access-date=2021-11-26|archive-date=2021-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211126153110/https://www.ebrd.com/downloads/news/MoU_EC-EIB-EIF-EBRD_Final_MB_formatting.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=The European Investment Bank {{!}} Fact Sheets on the European Union {{!}} European Parliament|url=https://www.europarl.europa.eu/factsheets/en/sheet/17/the-european-investment-bank|access-date=2021-04-21|website=www.europarl.europa.eu|language=en|archive-date=2021-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211126153623/https://www.europarl.europa.eu/factsheets/en/sheet/17/the-european-investment-bank|dead-url=no}}</ref>，為全球最大的[[超國家主義_(國際關係)|超國家]]貸款機構之一。<ref>{{Cite book|last=Putten|first=Maartje van|url=https://www.worldcat.org/oclc/760073184|title=Policing the banks : accountability mechanisms for the financial sector|date=2008|publisher=McGill-Queen's University Press|isbn=978-0-7735-7665-0|location=Montréal [Québec]|oclc=760073184}}</ref>

==历史==
是[[欧盟|欧盟]]的金融机构，1958年根据《[[罗马条约|罗马条约]]》创立，总部在[[卢森堡|卢森堡]]，同时，在布鲁塞尔、巴黎、罗马、赫尔辛基、雅典、柏林、里斯本、伦敦、马德里、华沙、伊斯坦布尔、布加勒斯特、突尼斯、达喀尔、拉巴特、内罗毕、法兰西堡、悉尼、比勒陀利亚和开罗设有办事处。

